Customer must reproduce, on all copies made by or for Customer, and must not remove, alter or obscure in any way all proprietary rights notices (including copyright notices) of Ironman Software, LLC on or within the copies of the Ironman Software, LLC Software and the Documentation furnished by Ironman Software, LLC to Customer.

