(c) Customer has no right to distribute, sublicense, lease, rent, loan or otherwise transfer the Product Source Code or the Modifications to any other person anywhere in the world; and

(d) Ironman Software, LLC is under no obligation to provide any Support Services in respect of any Modifications not provided directly by Ironman Software, LLC (support will only be provided in respect of the original compiled version of the Ironman Software, LLC Software).

