7.2 The Support Services do not include services provided by Ironman Software, LLC relating to or resulting from:
(a) Product Source Code with Modifications;

(b) misuse of the Ironman Software, LLC Software or failure to use the Ironman Software, LLC Software in accordance with the related Documentation;

