(d) support of prior releases or versions of the Ironman Software, LLC Software after six months from the date Ironman Software, LLC offered a Major Version to Customer.

7.3 Customer must renew its Support Subscription prior to the expiry of the then current period to maintain continuous support. Renewals can be made via the Ironman Software, LLC Store and require payment of a Support Subscription Fee.
